trans-unit.source: Specifies the context keyword for a class or member.
trans-unit.target: 指定類別或成員的內容關鍵字。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property value.
trans-unit.target: 根據預設，類別的 Help 關鍵字由提供<xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>屬性值。</xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.
trans-unit.target: 成員的完整名稱之類型的宣告屬性，再加上本身的屬性名稱是給定的 Help 關鍵字。

trans-unit.source: For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> control.
trans-unit.target: 例如，請考慮<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>屬性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>控制項。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class inherits the property.
trans-unit.target: 類別關鍵字會是"System.Windows.Forms.Button"，但<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>property 關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text"，因為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName>類別，而非<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>類別本身;<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>類別繼承的屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".
trans-unit.target: 相反地，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>類別中，因此其關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult"。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at HelpKeywordAttribute.
trans-unit.target: 當 [說明] 系統取得關鍵字時，它會先查看 HelpKeywordAttribute。

trans-unit.source: At the class level, it will return the string specified by the HelpKeywordAttribute.
trans-unit.target: 在類別層級，它會傳回 HelpKeywordAttribute 所指定的字串。

trans-unit.source: This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.
trans-unit.target: 這不會使用有問題，仍會反映實際完整名稱的宣告型別，以及成員名稱之類型的成員。

trans-unit.source: This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性支援具有相關聯的一般文件不同說明 Id 但的強型別的類別。
